<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>Document</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="../css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
	<!-- @import "header.kit" -->
	<div class="container">
		<div class="takeBox">
			<nav class="tekeBox__nav">
				<a href="index.kit" class="takeBox__nav-text">Home</a>
				<a href="#" class="takeBox__nav-text active">TakeBox Subscription</a>
			</nav>
			<div class="takeBox__top">
				<div class="takeBox__top-img"></div>
				<div class="takeBox__top__subscription">
					<div class="takeBox__top__subscription-title">TakeBox Subscription</div>
					<div class="takeBox__top__subscription-cost">$19.99</div>
					<form class="takeBox__top__subscription__form">
						<div class="takeBox__top__subscription__form__slider">
							<div class="takeBox__top__subscription__form__slider-text">Size</div>
							<select>
								<option>Men's - S</option>
								<option>Men's - M</option>
								<option>Men's - X</option>
								<option>Women's - S</option>
								<option>Women's - M</option>
								<option>Women's - X</option>
							</select>
						</div>
						<div class="takeBox__top__subscription__form__subscribe">
							<input type="checkbox" class="takeBox__top__subscription__form__subscribe-checkbox">
							<div class="takeBox__top__subscription__form__subscribe__input">
								<div class="takeBox__top__subscription__form__subscribe__input-title">1 Box Per Month</div>
								<div class="takeBox__top__subscription__form__subscribe__input-subtitle">1 monthly recurring payment of $19.99</div>
							</div>	
						</div>
						<a href="#" class="takeBox__top__subscription__form__slider-btn">SUBSCRIBE NOW</a>
					</form>
				<div class="takeBox__top__subscription-text">Stock will be despatched to you as soon as we receive it from our supplier.</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="takeBox__main">
				<div class="takeBox__main-title">Description</div>
				<div class="takeBox__main-text">
					<p>Guaranteed 4-7 items in every box from your favourite fandoms! You’re sure to get a cool t-shirt, collectibles, quirky gifts and so much more!</p>
					<p>A whole lot of mystery every single month, for as little as £19.99! Go get your Geek On!</p>
					<p>How it works?</p>
					<p>Pick your Subscription - Start your subscription by selecting your t-shirt size. There’s a size guide to help you make your selection. Don’t worry if you get this wrong the first time, our team will be there to help get it right for you. Create an Account - First time subscribers will have to create an account. Don’t worry we’ve made it easy for you and can be set up through social login to save you time. Through your account you’ll be able to manage your subscription, get regular updates as well as be the first to know about new product launches, our exclusives and personalised offers! You’re all set! - Once you’ve completed the above, we’ll ship out your first month’s box as soon as possible. We ship our boxes between the 10-20th of every month so stay tuned for alerts on despatch. Get involved on our Social!</p>
					<p>Share your unboxings with us by tagging us in your post on Facebook, Twitter and Instagram using #takebox. We’ll share our favourite pictures so stay social for a chance to get featured.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="takeBox-reviews"></div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<!-- @import "footer.kit" -->
</body>
</html>